<D>__{"sense and sensibility" screenplay by emma thompson based on the novel by jane austen}
<L>__{exterior open roads night title sequence}
<A>__{a series of traveling shots. a well dressed, pompous looking individual (john dashwood, 35) is making an urgent journey on horseback. he looks anxious.}
<L>__{exterior norland park england march 1800 night}
<A>__{silence. norland park, a large country house built in the early part of the eighteenth century, lies in the moonlit parkland.}
<L>__{interior norland park mr dashwood's bedroom night}
<A>__{in the dim light shed by candles we see a bed in which a man (mr dashwood, 52) lies his skin waxy, his breathing laboured. around him two silhouettes move and murmur, their clothing susurrating in the deathly hush. doctors. a woman (mrs dashwood, 50) sits by his side, holding his hand, her eyes never leaving his face.}
