<P>__{(urgent)}
<D>__{is john not yet arrived?}
<C>__{mrs dashwood}
<D>__{we expect him at any moment, dearest.}
<A>__{mr dashwood looks anguished.}
<C>__{mr dashwood}
<D>__{the girls i have left so little.}
<C>__{mrs dashwood}
<D>__{shh, hush, henry.}
<C>__{mr dashwood}
<D>__{elinor will try to look after you all, but make sure she finds a good husband. the men are such noodles hereabouts, little wonder none has pleased her.}
<A>__{they smile at each other. mrs dashwood is just managing to conceal her fear and grief}
<C>__{mrs dashwood}
